Consider the following recursive function fun(x, y). What is the value of fun(4, 3)

 

int fun(int x, int y) 

{

  if (x == 0)

    return y;

  return fun(x - 1,  x + y);

} 

A
13
B
12
C
9
D
10
Answer:--A
Explanation
The function fun() calculates and returns ((1 + 2 â€¦ + x-1 + x) +y) which is x(x+1)/2 + y.
